        }
      }
    },
    "Apple's Bonjour Sleep Proxy service is an open source[1] component of zero configuration networking, designed to assist in reducing power consumption of networked electronic devices.[2] A device acting as a sleep proxy server will respond to Multicast DNS queries for another, compatible device which has gone into low power mode. The low-power-mode device remains asleep while the sleep proxy server responds to any Multicast DNS queries.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple's Bonjour Sleep Proxy service is an open source[1] component of zero configuration networking, designed to assist in reducing power consumption of networked electronic devices.[2] A device acting as a sleep proxy server will respond to Multicast DNS queries for another, compatible device which has gone into low power mode. The low-power-mode device remains asleep while the sleep proxy server responds to any Multicast DNS queries."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "El servicio Bonjour Sleep Proxy de Apple es un componente de código abierto de la red de configuración cero, diseñado para reducir el consumo de energía de los dispositivos electrónicos en red. Un dispositivo que actúa como servidor Sleep Proxy responde a las consultas Multicast DNS por otro dispositivo compatible que ha entrado en modo de bajo consumo."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Le service Bonjour Sleep Proxy d'Apple est un composant open source de la mise en réseau sans configuration, conçu pour réduire la consommation d'énergie des appareils électroniques en réseau. Un appareil agissant comme serveur Sleep Proxy répond aux requêtes Multicast DNS pour un autre appareil compatible en mode veille."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apples Bonjour Sleep Proxy-Dienst ist eine Open-Source-Komponente der Zero-Configuration-Netzwerke, die den Stromverbrauch vernetzter elektronischer Geräte reduzieren soll. Ein Gerät, das als Sleep Proxy-Server fungiert, antwortet auf Multicast-DNS-Anfragen für ein anderes kompatibles Gerät im Energiesparmodus."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "AppleのBonjour Sleep Proxyサービスは、ゼロコンフィギュレーションネットワーキングのオープンソースコンポーネントで、ネットワーク接続された電子機器の消費電力削減を支援するよう設計されています。Sleep Proxyサーバーとして機能するデバイスは、低電力モードに入った互換デバイスに代わってMulticast DNSクエリに応答します。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "Apple的Bonjour Sleep Proxy服务是零配置网络的开源组件，旨在帮助降低联网电子设备的功耗。充当Sleep Proxy服务器的设备将代替已进入低功耗模式的兼容设备响应Multicast DNS查询。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Beats Transfer Protocol for discovering and configuring Beats audio products including headphones, earbuds, and speakers.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
