    "RFB (remote framebuffer) is a simple protocol for remote access to graphical user interfaces. Because it works at the framebuffer level it is applicable to all windowing systems and applications, including Microsoft Windows, macOS and the X Window System. RFB is the protocol used in Virtual Network Computing (VNC) and its derivatives.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB (remote framebuffer) is a simple protocol for remote access to graphical user interfaces. Because it works at the framebuffer level it is applicable to all windowing systems and applications, including Microsoft Windows, macOS and the X Window System. RFB is the protocol used in Virtual Network Computing (VNC) and its derivatives."
          }
        },
        "es": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB (remote framebuffer) es un protocolo simple para acceso remoto a interfaces gráficas de usuario. Al funcionar a nivel de framebuffer, es aplicable a todos los sistemas de ventanas y aplicaciones, incluyendo Microsoft Windows, macOS y X Window System. RFB es el protocolo utilizado en Virtual Network Computing (VNC) y sus derivados."
          }
        },
        "fr": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB (remote framebuffer) est un protocole simple pour l'accès à distance aux interfaces graphiques. Fonctionnant au niveau du framebuffer, il est applicable à tous les systèmes de fenêtrage et applications, y compris Microsoft Windows, macOS et le système X Window. RFB est le protocole utilisé dans Virtual Network Computing (VNC) et ses dérivés."
          }
        },
        "de": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB (Remote Framebuffer) ist ein einfaches Protokoll für den Fernzugriff auf grafische Benutzeroberflächen. Da es auf Framebuffer-Ebene arbeitet, ist es auf alle Fenstersysteme und Anwendungen anwendbar, einschließlich Microsoft Windows, macOS und das X Window System. RFB ist das Protokoll, das in Virtual Network Computing (VNC) und seinen Derivaten verwendet wird."
          }
        },
        "ja": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB（リモートフレームバッファ）は、グラフィカルユーザーインターフェースへのリモートアクセスのためのシンプルなプロトコルです。フレームバッファレベルで動作するため、Microsoft Windows、macOS、X Window Systemを含むすべてのウィンドウシステムとアプリケーションに適用できます。RFBはVirtual Network Computing（VNC）およびその派生で使用されるプロトコルです。"
          }
        },
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "RFB（远程帧缓冲）是一种用于远程访问图形用户界面的简单协议。由于它在帧缓冲级别工作，适用于所有窗口系统和应用程序，包括Microsoft Windows、macOS和X Window System。RFB是Virtual Network Computing（VNC）及其衍生产品使用的协议。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
    "Roku External Control Protocol (ECP) for discovering and controlling Roku streaming devices on the local network.": {
      "extractionState": "manual",
      "localizations": {
        "en": {
